songs.title: Insufficient Funds
songs.lyrics:
[Hook]
Your account is closed for insufficient funds
(I wish we could have this on the DVD, Lord
We got a sitch')

Your account is closed for insufficient funds
(Can you hear my little snaps?)

Your account is closed for insufficient funds
Your account is closed for insufficient funds
(Wait, you want me to say that too?
You can put that in—)

Your account is closed, wait
Your account is closed for insufficient funds
